{"tid":2044548,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚惠珠：唔立「國安法」，對唔住14億人","createTime":"2020-05-31T07:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T13:49:49.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"87a46a6572f2bbf1454d0eb0b9e088ee5bb5f0e9","tid":2044548,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T07:28:55.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）人大日前通過在香港制定「港版國安法」，基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠出席《無綫新聞》節目「講清講楚」，稱立法符合「法理情」，批評有人癱瘓立法會，街上發生縱火、汽油彈和私刑，中央不能袖手旁觀，認為立法屬合理，<span style=\"color: red;\">「唔採取行動，對唔住14億人。」</span><br />\n<br />\n譚惠珠稱，今次立法是因為有一小撮人影響了全部港人，<span style=\"color: red;\">又稱美國其實都有11條國安法</span>，指立法從來不屬地區體制的權力，必然在人大手上。在節目中，譚惠珠不斷引用法律條文，包括國家憲法和《基本法》等，稱今次立法是按國家憲法立法，23條的原意是在撰寫《基本法》時國內有反革命法，所以才決定讓香港自行立法。她更稱，23條立法的權力其實同在中央，並不是香港高度自治的範圍。<br />\n<br />\n對於「港版國安法」有可能導致人大釋法，譚惠珠認為釋法「不是咩新嘢」。...<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073981/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073981%2F&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdDkC3bY0i4P88JjHF8GLL0M%3D&h=4f22cada\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073981%2F&h=2e8640a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073981/</a>"},{"pid":"c00980ada2a9580c839878029918f995fca91a11","tid":2044548,"uid":242537,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T07:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hcQK8jw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhcQK8jw.jpg&h=1f484ae0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08efb63b11b02e1743a4188f55eb617f08916ee8","tid":2044548,"uid":205162,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T07:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tCogZrg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtCogZrg.gif&h=468cd019&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"008563e3a6d482e64f001e4911bb66f78a54fdc0","tid":2044548,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20